Quest._questDescription: Robin, the local carpenter, lives north of town. In exchange for raw materials and money, she'll construct new buildings on your farm. You'll need her to build a coop or barn so that you can raise animals.
It seems that the mine elevator is still functional. It will allow you to quickly return to any elevator doors you've discovered. A deeper expedition might be in order.

I am looking for someone to bring me 4 Copper Ores, as part of a local geological survey.    -Clint

- 180g on delivery.
- You can keep the ores after Clint inspects them.
Quest.targetMessage: You brought the ores I requested! Great.#$b#These ores look to be of good quality... You can keep them, of course. I just wanted to see how the local geology is doing.#$b#...And here's your payment, as promised.
